The paper proposes a graph convolutional neural network based model for social recommendation, which involves modeling the information diffusion process in social networks. This suggests that the paper could belong to several arXiv CS sub-categories, including cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.SOC (Computational Social Science), and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Among these, cs.LG is the most likely category as the paper focuses on a machine learning model, while cs.SI and cs.IR are also likely categories as the paper deals with social networks and recommendation systems. cs.SOC and cs.AI are less likely categories, but still possible as the paper involves computational social science and artificial intelligence techniques.
